    <item>
      <title>印度央行表示不急于降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/india-central-bank-holds-key-rate-sticks-with-hawkish-stance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀仍远高于目标，印度央行周四坚持其鹰派政策立场，这表明印度央行在今年晚些时候之前并不急于降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/india-central-bank-holds-key-rate-sticks-with-hawkish-stance</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 04:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
