    <item>
      <title>印度期待瑞士和挪威投资1000亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/india-eyes-100-billion-investment-deal-with-switzerland-norway</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度即将敲定一项史无前例的贸易协议，少数欧洲国家可能会在 15 年内投资多达 1000 亿美元，以换取更容易与世界上人口最多的国家进行贸易准入。对此事的了解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/india-eyes-100-billion-investment-deal-with-switzerland-norway</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:50:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
